dct_title_s: Nord-Ostpreussens : Norden vom Kurischen Haff bis zur Szeszuppe / Blochplan. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Panel title. Map shows actual place names and historical German place names from 1938 to 1945. Russian place names are given in Cyrillic and Latin script. Index on verso.
